{"type": "article", "id": 23450, "title": "底座相连的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150440MfJo27OI9yvDF6Tg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏台灯有一个有趣的名字 Alpha&amp;Beta，灯的底座相连而灯头分离，很有情景感，似乎象征了人和人之间的关系。灯头的朝向角度并不一致，因而这盏灯也不是完全对称的，可以进行多种解读。灯的底座用 Polycarbonate（聚碳酸酯）材料制作，可以选择黑、白、金三种颜色。设计方来自新加坡的一个成立于 2006 年设计品牌 Munkii，<a href=\"http://www.munkii.com.sg/alpha-beta-dimension.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150438SAbhi7tnreOj5Yof.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150439VSCjoYtWeKX5skz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150439WhtdL91D6HUI0GMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150439eZCv95uHQ7VBhwYb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}